refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;
variables
An array of any of the strings REQUEST_URI, PHP_SELF, SCRIPT_NAME and SCRIPT_FILENAME. Other values trigger an exception, and Phar::mungServer is case-sensitive.

&reftitle.errors;


 Throws UnexpectedValueException if any problems are
 found with the passed in data.

  &reftitle.examples;



    A Phar::mungServer example


<?php
// example stub
Phar::mungServer(array('REQUEST_URI'));
Phar::webPhar();
__HALT_COMPILER();
?>
